'''San Tojalon''' is a [[monster]] fought during the [[Legends' Quest]]. He is one of the three spirits found in the lower levels [[Legends caverns]] and must be defeated in order to gather all the pieces of the [[A red crystal|heart crystal]] used for the source of the spring water.

The Other spirits are called [[Ranalph Devere]] and [[Irvig Senay]].

==Locations==
*[[Legends caverns]]

